data.description: Three bedroom home with two bathrooms. The home is spacious (1,288 sq ft). Very nice living room with fireplace. Kitchen with plenty of counter top space, cabinets, and dish washer. Includes stove, refrigerator, washer and dryer hookups. Bathroom with his and her sinks. Walk-in closet in master bedroom. large backyard with a fence. New roof on property. Offered by broker, OKC Home Realty Services, LLC.
